Workflow.Name: Admin | Sync Template v3 (Desktop flow runs)
Workflow.Description: This flow gets desktop flow run history and session details. Turning on this flow is optional, and we recommended that you do so only if you're using desktop flows in your tenant and are interested in getting a tenant-wide overview.
